BET Awards 2017 Red Carpet Arrivals: Kat Graham, Dascha Polanco, and More Stars

The stars are coming out to play, on the red carpet that is. It’s finally time for the 2017 BET Awards and some of your fave celebrities are arriving at the annual show to celebrate…
